1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

CVSS v3 7.5
ATTENTION: Exploitable remotely/low attack complexity
Vendor: Mitsubishi Electric
Equipment: MELSEC and MELIPC Series
Vulnerabilities: Uncontrolled Resource Consumption, Improper Handling of Length Parameter Inconsistency, Improper Input Validation

2. RISK EVALUATION
Successful exploitation of these vulnerabilities could allow a remote attacker to cause a denial-of-service condition. Recovery requires a system reset.
